**[警告][设计] AccessRecorder core 需要真正的 move-only 所有权语义**

证据：`ObjectAccessRecorder`/`StreamAccessRecorder` 声明了 `ObjectAccessRecorder(ObjectAccessRecorder &&) noexcept = default` 这类默认 move，但内部成员 `AccessRecorder core_` 没有删除 copy、也没有自定义 move；当前代码又在 `object_client_impl.cpp` 和 `client_worker_sc_service_impl.cpp` 多处使用 `std::make_shared<ObjectAccessRecorder>(AccessRecorder::Object(...))` / `std::make_shared<StreamAccessRecorder>(AccessRecorder::Stream(...))`。

问题：`AccessRecorder` 析构函数有 `!isRecord_` 时打印 `Not call AccessRecorder::Record()` 的所有权语义，但它仍然是隐式可拷贝对象。facade 默认 move 时会按成员初始化移动 `core_`，在 `AccessRecorder` 没有 move 构造的情况下会退化为 copy；moved-from 临时对象析构时仍然认为自己未记录。

影响：sampled-in 的异步 object access 或 worker stream access 会在正常记录前/后产生误报警告，日志基础设施自身污染日志；更糟的是，后续维护者仍可意外复制 `AccessRecorder` core，造成两个 recorder 共享一次采样决策但各自析构/记录状态不一致。

建议：把 `AccessRecorder` 明确做成 move-only RAII core：删除 copy 构造/赋值，自定义 move 构造/赋值转移 `handleName_`、`handleType_`、`beg_`、`shouldRecord_`、`isRecord_`，并把 moved-from 对象标记为已处理，保证析构不报警。facade 的默认 move 才有正确语义。

示例：

```cpp
class AccessRecorder {
public:
    explicit AccessRecorder(AccessRecorderKey key);
    ~AccessRecorder();

    AccessRecorder(const AccessRecorder &) = delete;
    AccessRecorder &operator=(const AccessRecorder &) = delete;

    AccessRecorder(AccessRecorder &&other) noexcept
        : beg_(other.beg_), handleName_(std::move(other.handleName_)), handleType_(other.handleType_),
          isRecord_(other.isRecord_), shouldRecord_(other.shouldRecord_)
    {
        other.isRecord_ = true;
        other.shouldRecord_ = false;
    }

    AccessRecorder &operator=(AccessRecorder &&other) noexcept
    {
        if (this == &other) {
            return *this;
        }
        beg_ = other.beg_;
        handleName_ = std::move(other.handleName_);
        handleType_ = other.handleType_;
        isRecord_ = other.isRecord_;
        shouldRecord_ = other.shouldRecord_;
        other.isRecord_ = true;
        other.shouldRecord_ = false;
        return *this;
    }
};
```

验证：补充单测覆盖 `std::make_shared<ObjectAccessRecorder>(AccessRecorder::Object(...))` 和 `std::make_shared<StreamAccessRecorder>(AccessRecorder::Stream(...))` 的 sampled-in 路径，断言正常 `Record()` 不产生 `Not call AccessRecorder::Record()` 警告；同时用编译期断言确认 `AccessRecorder` 不可拷贝、可移动。

